snippet.textDisplay:
Apnader arrangements khub e darun, amar sei khomota nei seta k judge korar, Puro gaan er arrangements khub bhalo, 
Ami kolkatar basinda amar roots holo chottogram Potiya r amar bari te sobai akhono motamuti sittainga bhasay kotha bole ! Tai jini gaan ta geyechen tar  sittainga accent niye amar appotti ache! 
Sittainga bhashar accent tai sittainga bhashar asol bhalobashar jaayga! Amar motey apnader arektu research kora uchit chilo eta niye ! Hote pare apnara jara Sittainga bhasha bolte parena tader jonno ektu sohoj kore niyechen kintu seta hole bhashar madhurjo ta chole jaay! 
Jaihok overall darun arrangement aro sittainga gaan sonar oppekkhay roilam.
Love from Kolkata ❤️
